Tonight I will be helping Raise Money for @gktwvillage .. I’ll be reading to the Children at 7pm eat .. if your interested in donating Text44321  and if your interested in watching the live stream go to my story and swipe up ❤️❤️❤️ #givingtuesdaynow 
Each month more than 700 children are waiting for their wishes due COVID-19, but on this #GivingTuesdayNow  we're showing them the hope and magic that's in store for them at the Village. Join us to help #givehopetowishes

node.text: Hey guys! It’s me Cameron 💙 I’m 2 months old today!!! These past two months have been so great! I have the best big brother ever .. he plays with me and helps mommy take care of me .. I can’t wait until I can run and play with him! My mommy and daddy are so loving! I love when they give me a million kisses 🥰 I’m so loved ! I just found my hands and feet and love smiling .. I’m not big into tummy time ..but everyone says I’m pretty strong ! My mommy said we’re gonna work on grabbing soon .. I love sensory books and sensory toys .. they make me smile .. I love going outside with my brother and relaxing in the pool ! Alright that’s it for my update I’m gonna go take a nap ! Thanks for following my growing journey and supporting my mommy !!
